==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Placer
<hw>Plac"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.]</ety> <def>A
deposit of earth, sand, or gravel, containing valuable mineral in
particles, especially by the side of a river, or in the bed of a
mountain torrent.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

